{
  "stem": "27031.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father was hiding at his place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he took me down there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was a Ukrainian village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let me put some into that before I go any farther.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our area was Ukrainian villages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then we had three villages, Czech, Czech villages.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The father always told us if you have a problem, the Czech villagers are safer to the Jews, or friendlier to the Jews, to always run to a Czech village.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Czech villages, was three of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were in a radius of 20 miles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But father was in the Ukrainian village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was hiding there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I was with father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A few days later brother, Jack, came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we were reunited.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were hiding in the barn, and that them people, they fed us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know if father paid, maybe, in gold or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I couldn't-- I really didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just hide in the straw piles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, like I said, the local population knew who survived, and they were hunting for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They knew that father and two of us were living.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were hunting somewhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't know where we were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had to-- we couldn't go out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So all we did is lay in the barns, in the straw piles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Finally, things got very hot, as we used to say it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That the Nazi sympathizers were tracking closer to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So father said we got to run.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES] So Jack and I, we took off at night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And father said-- I cannot recollect exactly where he's going to meet us, somehow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But as we walked out, Jack and I, we were hiding in that Ukrainian village, different places, straw piles.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
